    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "But that's actually what's important to me: I can pass `extra_args=['--c', 'some code']` to the kernel launch function and let `Popen` escape the code argument. Currently, I have to do `extra_args=['--c=\"my code\"']` and worry about everything being escaped properly. Painful, especially on Windows.\n"
